    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="I want to edit the appearance of my profile screen (cover image, Featured, etc.)" class="article-title">
          I want to edit the appearance of my profile screen (cover image, Featured, etc.)
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><h2>Edit cover image</h2>
<p>You can upload a cover image to display in your profile header from the pencil mark at the top of your profile page.</p>
<p>You can upload JPEG/PNG/GIF images up to 8 MB.<br>The recommended aspect ratio is 2:1.<br>Please note that we won't accept R-18 images or works prohibited by the guidelines.<br>These images will be unpublished right away.</p>
<h2>Edit Featured</h2>
<p>The featured works displayed on your profile can be edited from the Featured settings on your profile page.</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

